data.meta_description: Kevin Knowles II (3) DB - 2023: Appeared in 13 games with three starts…recorded 31 tackles, including 0.5 for loss, three pass breakups and one quarterback h...
data.text: Appeared in 13 games with three starts…recorded 31 tackles, including 0.5 for loss, three pass breakups and one quarterback hurry…registered career-high eight tackles, 0.5 for loss, in 31-24 victory at Clemson…opened season with two tackles in 45-24 victory vs. No. 5 LSU…had one solo stop in 66-13 win vs. Southern Miss…made five solo tackles and one pass breakup in 31-29 win at Boston College…registered three tackles in back-to-back-to-back games, reaching that mark in 39-17 win vs. Virginia Tech, 41-3 win vs. Syracuse and 38-20 win vs. No. 16 Duke…made one tackle in 41-16 win at Wake Forest…recorded two tackles, one pass breakup and one quarterback hurry in 24-7 win at Pitt…registered one pass breakup in 27-20 victory vs. Miami…made three tackles in Orange Bowl vs. No. 6 Georgia…also saw action in 24-15 victory at Florida and in ACC Championship Game victory vs. No. 14 Louisville.
